She stood there hoping Megatron wouldn't hit her again.  Her face had 
finally healed from the last time.
"Commander, This is Drillbit.  He helped us rescue Quickstrike.  He 
has been faithful to you this whole time." as she tried to speak on 
Drillbit's behalf.
